@startuml Architecture_MonitoringVehicles
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam linetype ortho

title Diagram Arsitektur: GPS Vehicle Monitoring System

frame "IoT Devices Layer" {
  component "GPS Device 1\n(Android/IoT)" as Device1
  component "GPS Device 2\n(Android/IoT)" as Device2
  component "GPS Device N\n(Android/IoT)" as DeviceN
  note bottom of Device1
    Mengirim location setiap
    30 detik ke backend via HTTPS
    Format: JSON GPS data
  end note
}

frame "Presentation Layer" {
  component "Web Browser\n(Vue.js 3)" as Frontend
  component "Interactive Map\n(Leaflet.js)" as Map
  component "Responsive UI\n(Dashboard, Vehicles,\nGeofences)" as UI

  Frontend --> Map : Render
  Frontend --> UI : Render

  note bottom of Frontend
    - SPA (Single Page Application)
    - Real-time polling (5s interval)
    - Local storage untuk token JWT
    - Running on port 3000
  end note
}

frame "API Layer / Backend" {
  component "Express.js Server\n(REST API)" as Server
  component "Authentication\nMiddleware\n(JWT Verification)" as Auth
  component "Request Validation" as Validation
  component "Rate Limiting\n(DDoS Protection)" as RateLimit

  Server --> Auth : Protect routes
  Server --> Validation : Validate input
  Server --> RateLimit : Limit requests

  note bottom of Server
    - RESTful API endpoints
    - Async/await handlers
    - Error handling
    - Logging & monitoring
    - Running on port 5000
  end note
}

frame "Business Logic Layer" {
  component "Location Controller\n(GPS Update Handler)" as LocController
  component "Vehicle Controller\n(CRUD Operations)" as VehicleController
  component "Geofence Controller\n(CRUD + Retrieval)" as GeoController
  component "Auth Controller\n(Login/Register)" as AuthController

  note bottom of LocController
    - Menerima POST /api/location
    - Trigger geofence detection
    - Call geofencing logic
  end note
}

frame "Geofencing Logic" {
  component "Ray Casting\nAlgorithm\n(Point-in-Polygon)" as Algorithm
  component "Violation Detection\n& Logger" as ViolationDetector

  LocController --> Algorithm : Check point vs polygon
  Algorithm --> ViolationDetector : Violation result

  note bottom of Algorithm
    - Matematical algorithm
    - O(n) complexity
    - Accurate detection
    - Handle edge cases
  end note
}

frame "Data Layer" {
  component "MongoDB\n(NoSQL Database)" as DB
  component "Collections:" as Collections

  Collections --|> "users" :
  Collections --|> "vehicles" :
  Collections --|> "geofences" :
  Collections --|> "locationlogs" :
  Collections --|> "notificationlogs" :

  note bottom of DB
    - Document-based storage
    - Geospatial indexing
    - High availability (Replica Set)
    - Secure authentication
  end note
}

frame "Notification Service" {
  component "N8N Workflow\nOrchestrator" as N8N
  component "Email Service\n(SMTP)" as EmailService
  component "Telegram Bot\nAPI" as TelegramBot
  component "WhatsApp\nBusiness API" as WhatsAppAPI

  N8N --> EmailService : Send email
  N8N --> TelegramBot : Send message
  N8N --> WhatsAppAPI : Send message

  note bottom of N8N
    - Webhook receiver
    - Async workflow
    - Decoupled from backend
    - Multi-channel support
    - Retry mechanism
  end note
}

frame "External Services" {
  component "OpenStreetMap\n(Map Tiles)" as OSM
  component "Third-party\nNotification APIs" as ThirdParty
  note bottom of OSM
    - Free map tiles
    - Used by Leaflet
  end note
}

Device1 -.-> Server : HTTPS POST\n/api/location
Device2 -.-> Server : HTTPS POST
DeviceN -.-> Server : HTTPS POST

Frontend -.-> Server : REST API\nHTTPS requests
Frontend -.-> OSM : Fetch map tiles
Frontend -.-> Map : Render

Server -.-> LocController : Route requests
Server -.-> VehicleController : Route requests
Server -.-> GeoController : Route requests
Server -.-> AuthController : Route requests

ViolationDetector -.-> ViolationDetector : Create N8N\nwebhook trigger

ViolationDetector -.-> N8N : POST Webhook\nViolation data

LocController -.-> DB : Query/Insert
VehicleController -.-> DB : Query/Insert/Update/Delete
GeoController -.-> DB : Query/Insert/Update/Delete
AuthController -.-> DB : Query/Insert

Algorithm -.-> GeoController : Return boolean

N8N -.-> ThirdParty : Send notifications

note bottom
  **System Components Summary:**

  **Input**: GPS coordinates dari IoT devices
  **Processing**: Geofence violation detection
  **Storage**: MongoDB NoSQL database
  **Output**: Real-time dashboard + Notifications

  **Key Features:**
  ✓ Real-time vehicle tracking
  ✓ Polygon-based geofencing
  ✓ Multi-channel notifications
  ✓ Scalable architecture
  ✓ Secure JWT authentication
  ✓ Data isolation per user
  ✓ Comprehensive logging

  **Technologies Stack:**
  Frontend: Vue.js 3, Vite, Leaflet.js
  Backend: Node.js, Express.js
  Database: MongoDB
  Notifications: N8N
  Security: JWT, bcryptjs, CORS
end note

@enduml
